Judges in the trial of Dutch MP Geert Wilders are ordered to step down by an independent appeals panel, with the legal process now having to begin again. (BBC) (The Guardian) (AFP via The Sydney Morning Herald)Prominent Russian journalist Oleg Kashin for the Kommersant newspaper is attacked outside his home in Moscow. (Reuters) (RIA Novosti)A riot in the Pedrinhas prison in north-eastern Brazil results in eighteen prisoner deaths and a guard being wounded. (AFP via ABC News Australia)